              </para>
            </clause.desc>
            <clause.desc>
              <para>
                <text><emphasis style="italic">Clause 20</emphasis> provides for the transfer of employees of the current Electoral Commission to the new Electoral Commission, with their consent, on 1 October 2010.</text>
              </para>
            </clause.desc>
            <clause.desc>
