                    </para>
                  </item>
                </list>
                <list>
                  <item>
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes"/>
                    <para>
                      <text>as references to the new Electoral Commission on and from 1 October 2010 (except for the references in sections 28(2)(c) and 33(4) of the principal Act).</text>
                    </para>
                  </item>
                </list>
              </para>
            </clause.desc>
            <clause.desc>
              <para>
                <text><emphasis style="italic">Clause 22</emphasis> provides for the transfer of assets, records, liabilities, and debts of the Chief Electoral Office of the Ministry of Justice to the new Electoral Commission on 1 October 2010.</text>
              </para>
            </clause.desc>
            <clause.desc>
              <para>
