              </para>
            </clause.desc>
            <clause.desc>
              <para>
                <text><emphasis style="italic">Clauses 24 to 26</emphasis> deal with terms and conditions of employment, continuity of employment, and restriction of technical redundancy in respect of employees transferred to the new Electoral Commission from the current Electoral Commission or the Chief Electoral Office of the Ministry of Justice.</text>
